* This program enables ad-hoc tethering (wifi and bluetooth).
* This application requires root-permission on the device
*******************************************************************************
* Open Garden Wifi Tether shares the handset network connection 
* (GPRS/EDGE/UMTS/HSDPA), creating an ad-hoc Wifi Access HotSpot.
